      • createModelForTenant

        DmnModel createModelForTenant(DmnModel model)
        Model updates are typically additive but for the time being at least this is not enforced.
        Parameters:
        model - The new model.
        deploymentMessage - Message to store alongside the deployment for example including a change control reference (may be null).
        image - Graphical representation of the decision (may be null).
        tenantId - The tenant to create the model for.
        Returns:
        The requested model.
